            "text": "A five-minute daytime tapping practice from Day 23 of a 30-day sleep program. The script addresses the habit of overriding the body's energy and rest signals, pushing through when tired, treating rest as a reward rather than a rhythm. The reframe builds cooperation: moving when energy rises, pausing when it dips.",
